344
00:35:51,560 --> 00:35:54,520
Kau tahu kenapa
aku sangat menghormati seni debat?

345
00:35:56,560 --> 00:35:58,520
Karena, seperti semua seni,

346
00:35:58,600 --> 00:36:00,520
